to do anything

06:55.050 --> 06:57.170
that you cannot find
a way to do legally.

06:57.170 --> 07:00.140
If it lies with the girl, well,

07:00.140 --> 07:02.170
if this goes to trial,

07:02.170 --> 07:05.130
