07:13.150 --> 07:15.150
The skills needed
to be a board president

07:15.150 --> 07:17.200
differ from those needed
to be a rabbi.

07:17.200 --> 07:20.130
- You're the one
charged with rape.

07:20.130 --> 07:23.130
- And you now
consider me guilty, don't you?

07:23.130 --> 07:24.140
- I think
if you tell your story,

07:24.140 --> 07:26.110
you'll get convicted.

07:26.110 --> 07:28.190
Does the board know your story?
- No.

07:28.190 --> 07:31.130
I told them it was consensual,
which I maintain it was.

07:31.130 --> 07:35.110
I don't think
they need to know more.

07:35.110 --> 07:38.180
Eugene,
you just said

07:38.180 --> 07:40.160
