I'll be convicted.

07:40.160 --> 07:43.150
What if I don't testify?

07:43.150 --> 07:46.130
- I don't like your chances.

07:46.130 --> 07:52.080
- So, could you at least
meet with her civil attorney?

07:52.080 --> 07:54.090
- I'm not comfortable
with this at all.

07:54.090 --> 07:55.120
- Neither am I.

07:55.120 --> 07:56.150
But, see,
a man's freedom

07:56.150 --> 07:58.080
is on the line here.

07:58.080 --> 07:59.140
His life, even.

07:59.140 --> 08:01.170
This is a very beloved rabbi.

08:01.170 --> 08:03.230
- I thought you couldn't
do this in rape cases.

08:03.230 --> 08:05.180
Dig up old boyfriends
