The jury brought back a verdict.

43:03.230 --> 43:05.000
Go ask them.

43:05.000 --> 43:06.140
We have no comment.

43:06.140 --> 43:09.120
[reporters clamoring]

43:15.140 --> 43:17.030
- Thanks.

43:17.030 --> 43:18.170
- Yeah.

43:18.170 --> 43:22.040
Congratulations, I guess.

